{"tid":115174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太常「打手槍」會不舉、不孕？醫師：剛好相反","createTime":"2017-02-10T11:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T13:35:11.000Z","uid":53379,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41c61cfdcc7b14bdb043cae0c899f264cf7d35dd","tid":115174,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太常「打手槍」會不舉、不孕？醫師：剛好相反</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2016/12/bs61beyr9sj0e8rps25ty6i8lukhhd.png?fit=crop&amp;h=300&amp;q=100&amp;w=500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2016%2F12%2Fbs61beyr9sj0e8rps25ty6i8lukhhd.png%3Ffit%3Dcrop%26h%3D300%26q%3D100%26w%3D500&h=1c13d7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（中央社）<br />\n男性太常打手槍恐導致不舉、早洩、不孕，甚至可能導致攝護腺肥大？這些都是錯誤迷思，醫師表示，適度自慰不僅可提高精子品質，還可減少攝護腺結石及肥大風險。<br />\n<br />\n林口長庚醫院男性學及婦女泌尿科主任陳煜公布「台灣個人與兩性自慰行為大調查」，調查顯示，已婚者有高達8成4有自慰習慣，比單身者7成6還高，且與伴侶交往越久或結婚越久，有自慰習慣比例越高。<br />\n<br />\n陳煜說，自慰就像性愛，只是滿足性需求的方式之一，但臨床上卻常有患者對於自慰這件事抱有錯誤迷思，甚至有父親帶孩子求診，希望矯正孩子自慰慾望。<br />\n<br />\n過度自慰可能導致不舉及早洩？陳煜說，早洩與腦中血清素訊號有關，緊張、情緒激動也可能導致早洩，而勃起功能障礙則有可能是因壓力，也可能是老化、慢性病引發血管健康問題導致。<br />\n<br />\n自慰過多是否會導致不孕？這也是常見迷思，他指出，自慰不僅不會導致不孕，還能提高精子活動度及品質，有助提高受孕機會。<br />\n<br />\n此外，也有不少人誤以為自慰會導致睪丸癌、攝護腺肥大，甚至有腎虧、掉髮等問題，陳煜表示，自慰能排出體內細菌，也能避免精液中礦物質沉澱，可減少攝護腺結石或肥大風險，禿頭問題則和自慰無因果關係，雄性禿原因為男性荷爾蒙睪固酮旺盛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/56783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F56783&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HagHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8e937c7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/56783</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4238c4ea8628976a4a0945365775857416420df2","tid":115174,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"每日要打J出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9dbc979a6041833fd37116d99aee4b8cb0b718","tid":115174,"uid":46312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"召喚蕭巴單挑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522c30dd1dd0ca7f0665539fc0c6127e03b4bd96","tid":115174,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"調查顯示，已婚者有高達8成4有自慰習慣，比單身者7成6還高，且與伴侶交往越久或結婚越久，有自慰習慣比例越高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d138726a91c911c8b0584e927c59a04cc4525b27","tid":115174,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>調查顯示，已婚者有高達8成4有自慰習慣，比單身者7成6還高，且與伴侶交往越久或結婚越久，有自慰習慣比例越高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌得多都悶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978dc17472da28337cb5309d061d4147617fd20e","tid":115174,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75932d694c7c450c3dce81efc47a21f7d7dd7fc9","tid":115174,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994db5e1d0e30efd6b8bbadd98a9c3c3ee3f9f07","tid":115174,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"477c425948e14a15cd3422de56b76b382b7e2a1c","tid":115174,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我每日打1-3次，打左16年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知健康定唔健康啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想死</blockquote><br />\n你就快精盡人亡<